item.title: Kenny Wayne Shepherd talks Bobby Rush collaboration, Van Halen tour, Guitar Gear and More
item.description:
The Jeremy White Show welcomes blues guitar legend Kenny Wayne Shepherd!


KWS and Jeremy discussed the upcoming release of a record featuring Kenny Wayne Shepherd and Bobby Rush, as well as the evolution of blues music and the importance of capturing the essence of an amp's sound. They also shared their experiences with Van Halen's last tour and expressed dissatisfaction with the lack of innovation in guitar equipment... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/fc5087e4/podcast/rss
